      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/22/1",
      "text": [
        " سَمِعْتُهُ يَقُولُ: \"مَنْ أَتَى أَهْلَهُ فِي مُحَاقِ اَلشَّهْرِ فَلْيُسَلِّمْ لِسِقْطِ اَلْوَلَدِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4406 - Sulaiman bin Ja'far al-Ja'fari narrated from Abu al-Hasan Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as), that he said: \"Whoever approaches his wife during the waning phase of the moon, let him be prepared for the miscarriage of the child.\""
        ]
      }
